-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                 This is README for CudaBandwidthCal-v1.1.cu
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Objective: To calculate the bandwidth for pagebale/pinned memory from Host-to Device 
           and Device-to-Host for a given range in MB/s.


Compile and Execute :
------------------------

1. Compilation :

	Go in particular directory and type 'make'.

2. Execution :

2.1. If you want to run with default size just give ./ <executable>

2.2. If you want to run with data sizes of your choice and memory mode of default size then give

    <executable> <memmode: 0-pageable , 1-pinned> <Start data size in bytes> <End data size in bytes> <Increment value in bytes>



2.3 Output : Bandwidth in MB/s for a given data size
